1
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:02,320
I wanted to kill him right away.

2
00:01:04,080 --> 00:01:05,800
But I knew I couldn't.

3
00:01:06,720 --> 00:01:09,200
Because he's the only one who knows where Shengnan is.

4
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,080
If I killed him,

5
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,480
I'd never find Shengnan.

6
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,370
Since you found him,

7
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:15,280
why didn't you report it to the police again?

8
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,539
Would that do any good?

9
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:19,800
The Ghost Mother Gang case was closed a long time ago.

10
00:01:19,800 --> 00:01:21,660
They'd just turn me away if I went.

11
00:01:22,039 --> 00:01:23,440
Besides, I don't have any evidence.

12
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:25,440
Gu Dachuan won't admit to anything.

13
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:28,880
So I had to investigate it my own way.

14
00:01:31,039 --> 00:01:32,600
Let's go.

15
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,440
Come on.

16
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,780
I'll take you to the night market.

17
00:01:35,880 --> 00:01:37,280
Let's go buy some treats.

18
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:40,160
Since that day,

19
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,920
I've been watching their house every day.

20
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:43,800
Break it up.

21
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:44,640
It's a misunderstanding.

22
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,880
Break it up.

23
00:01:46,039 --> 00:01:47,500
It's a misunderstanding.

24
00:01:49,039 --> 00:01:50,880
Dad, I want a piggy sugar figure.

25
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,080
Be good, Tongtong.

26
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:53,539
Daddy will buy one for you.

27
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,880
One piggy sugar figure, please.

28
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:56,520
Coming right up.

29
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,400
I'll add extra white sesame seeds.

30
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,360
Just a moment.

31
00:01:59,039 --> 00:01:59,400
Take care.

32
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,080
Finally,

33
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,920
I came up with a plan.

34
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:22,200
How much is this, boss?

35
00:02:22,200 --> 00:02:22,880
Tongtong.

36
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:24,400
Tongtong.

37
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,040
I'll take one.

38
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:29,560
Here.

39
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,520
Do you want a sugar figure?

40
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,720
So you planned all of this

41
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:45,240
just so we would

42
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,240
investigate in the direction you wanted.

43
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:47,640
Right?

44
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:49,000
Yes.

45
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:52,650
That's why I copied the Ghost Mother Gang's methods.

46
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,560
It was the only way

47
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,360
to get you to reinvestigate the case.

48
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,360
Sit anywhere.

49
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,660
What do you want to eat?

50
00:03:14,760 --> 00:03:16,090
Let's sit down and talk.

51
00:03:17,120 --> 00:03:17,880
Long.

52
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:24,640
Who are you?

53
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,640
Do you want to know where your son is?

54
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,960
You kidnapped Tongtong.

55
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,560
You kidnapped my daughter eight years ago.

56
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,650
I'll let you have a taste of your own medicine.

57
00:03:39,079 --> 00:03:40,200
You've got the wrong person.

58
00:03:40,200 --> 00:03:41,320
When did I ever kidnap your daughter?

59
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,400
You've kidnapped so many people,

60
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:44,060
you probably don't remember.

61
00:03:46,600 --> 00:03:48,000
You kidnapped Tongtong,

62
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:49,329
and just came to find me?

63
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,800
Aren't you afraid

64
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,240
I'll call the police on you?

65
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,480
Go ahead and try,

66
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,460
if you ever want to see your son again.

67
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:57,880
Besides,

68
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,760
the police

69
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:04,620
probably already know you're Brother Long.

70
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:07,400
What do you want?

71
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,560
It's simple.

72
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:11,330
Give my daughter back to me,

73
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:14,300
and I'll give your son back to you.

74
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:15,360
It's been so many years.

75
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:17,040
Where am I supposed to find your daughter?

76
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,240
That's your problem.

77
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,200
If you want to see your son.

78
00:04:20,200 --> 00:04:22,130
Just take my daughter in exchange.

79
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:28,680
Wait.

80
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,040
How much do you want?

81
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,100
I can give it to you.

82
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,080
How much?

83
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,890
How much do you think your son is worth?

84
00:04:40,960 --> 00:04:42,020
My entire fortune.

85
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:42,920
I can give it all to you.

86
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,720
Your fortune.

87
00:04:44,080 --> 00:04:45,360
Keep it for yourself.

88
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:49,140
Consider it payment for your son's life.

89
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:53,320
I need to know

90
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:56,159
if Tongtong is really in your hands.

91
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,300
Eight o'clock.

92
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:00,000
I'll be waiting at your hideout.

93
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,380
Does it look familiar?

94
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,700
Give me a little more time.

95
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:22,810
I promise I can find your daughter.

96
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:25,420
Don't think you can fool me with just anyone.

97
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,040
On my daughter's back,

98
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,170
there is a birthmark the size of a bowl.

99
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,560
I'll give you seven days.

100
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,400
In seven days,

101
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,960
bring my daughter to me.

102
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,440
Since you promised him seven days,

103
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,040
why did you kill him?

104
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,280
Gu Dachuan is dead.

105
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,980
Gu Dachuan trafficked so many children.

106
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,440
He had no idea where your daughter

107
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:52,440
was sold.

108
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:54,360
So you flew into a rage

109
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,440
and killed him.

110
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,170
How did you kill him?

111
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:02,290
You don't actually think I killed him, do you?

112
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,160
Yes.

113
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,320
For the past eight years,

114
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:08,580
I've wanted to kill him every single day.

115
00:06:08,640 --> 00:06:10,240
But right now, the last person who wants him dead

116
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:10,960
is me.

117
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:13,840
Because only he knows where my daughter is.

118
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:14,640
If I killed him,

119
00:06:14,640 --> 00:06:16,240
I'd never find my Shengnan.

120
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,530
Gu Dachuan wanted his son so badly.

121
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,120
He wouldn't just say he couldn't find Shengnan

122
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,780
without even looking for her.

123
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:26,500
Where is Gu Yitong now?

124
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,480
Leng Fang.

125
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:31,040
Think carefully.

126
00:06:31,160 --> 00:06:32,560
If you confess now,

127
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,320
we can still fight for leniency.

128
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:35,680
I don't need leniency.

129
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,400
I just want my daughter back.

130
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,240
Hand over Gu Yitong,

131
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,880
and we'll do our best to find your daughter.

132
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,720
I know you two are good detectives,

133
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,040
but Gu Yitong is my only bargaining chip right now.

134
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:54,920
So I can't hand him over to you.

135
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,600
Since Gu Dachuan is dead,

136
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,200
you go find Shengnan for me.

137
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:01,840
I promise you.

138
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,860
Bring Shengnan back to me,

139
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:06,200
and I'll hand over Gu Yitong.

140
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,370
Can you guarantee Gu Yitong's safety?

141
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,160
Tongtong hasn't been found yet.

142
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,040
And now Dachuan is dead.

143
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:19,360
With just my son and me left,

144
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,760
how will we go on?

145
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,700
Mrs. Gu, please rest assured.

146
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:25,060
We'll do our best to catch the killer.

147
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,050
Mrs. Gu, please don't mind.

148
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,320
We're just

149
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,900
following procedure.

150
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:31,500
We have one last question.

151
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,840
After Mr. Gu left the shop that day,

152
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,240
what did you do?

153
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,800
That day,

154
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,810
I was with Yijun while he practiced piano.

155
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,560
We were just about to close up

156
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,560
when you arrived.

157
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,880
Thank you for your cooperation.

158
00:07:47,880 --> 00:07:50,409
I'll have a colleague drive you back shortly.

159
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,800
How did it go?

160
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,400
Leng Fang probably didn't kill Gu Dachuan,

161
00:08:08,400 --> 00:08:10,730
but she admitted to kidnapping Gu Yitong.

162
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,960
So where is Gu Yitong now?

163
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,440
She won't say.

164
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:16,480
She wants us to help find her daughter,

165
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,140
and only then will she tell us.

166
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:19,480
But Leng Fang

167
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:22,200
really doesn't have a motive to kill Gu Dachuan.

168
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,240
She set this all up

169
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:25,000
just to get her daughter back.

170
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:28,920
It makes no sense for her to kill someone at this crucial moment.

171
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,880
The killer must be someone else.

172
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:33,120
Do you think

173
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,840
the person who killed Gu Dachuan

174
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:37,280
could be the buyer of Leng Fang's daughter?

175
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:39,159
Gu Dachuan

176
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:41,500
knew where Leng Fang's daughter was.

177
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,169
According to Leng Fang,

178
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,880
Gu Dachuan agreed to help her find her daughter.

179
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:47,720
That means

180
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,800
Gu Dachuan very likely

181
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,400
knew where her daughter was.

182
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:53,600
But Gu Dachuan hadn't had the chance to find the buyer yet.

183
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,080
It looks like we need to re-examine

184
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,010
Gu Dachuan's social connections.

185
00:09:02,640 --> 00:09:04,280
Boss Gu is a really nice man.

186
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,920
He's family-oriented and warm-hearted.

187
00:09:05,920 --> 00:09:07,000
I really can't imagine

188
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,760
who would kill such a good man.

189
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:10,840
Bad things happen to good people.

190
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,240
To meet such a terrible fate...

191
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:13,840
Heaven really is blind.

192
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:15,560
Exactly.

193
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,240
Thank you for your cooperation.

194
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,460
So, where does Boss Gu usually go?

195
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,480
Boss Gu is usually busy at the shop.

196
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,600
He rarely goes out.

197
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:25,360
Even if he does go out,

198
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:27,360
he takes his wife and child with him.

199
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:29,920
Sir,

200
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,320
do you live here?

201
00:09:35,040 --> 00:09:36,680
Boss Gu from the wonton shop next door,

202
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:37,640
do you know him?

203
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,810
Did you know their youngest son went missing?

204
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,080
Did you see him yesterday?

205
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:58,960
Have there been any

206
00:09:58,960 --> 00:10:00,320
strangers looking for him recently?

207
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,880
Or was there anything

208
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:03,200
different from usual?

209
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,400
Their family is too noisy.

210
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:14,120
They play the piano until twelve every night.

211
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:17,820
It's been noisy for years.

212
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,760
I've gotten used to it.

213
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:24,360
But yesterday,

214
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:26,640
it was quiet,

215
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,000
so I couldn't sleep.

216
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,600
Officers,

217
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:38,800
is something the matter?

218
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:39,800
Sorry to intrude.

219
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,360
There were some details regarding Mr. Gu

220
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,690
that we didn't clarify.

221
00:10:43,760 --> 00:10:45,560
So we came to ask you again today.

222
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:47,740
Please come in.

223
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:55,860
Where is Yijun?

224
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,890
He's upstairs writing.

225
00:11:03,400 --> 00:11:04,120
Mrs. Gu,

226
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,480
let's just talk here.

227
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,080
Yijun.

228
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,840
Hello, Officer.

229
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,920
Are you here to see my mom again?

230
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,930
I wanted to see you, too.

231
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,320
Officer,

232
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,120
you will catch

233
00:11:34,120 --> 00:11:35,640
the one who killed my dad,

234
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:36,720
right?

235
00:11:40,600 --> 00:11:41,730
We definitely will.

236
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:44,880
Can I ask you a few questions?

237
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:54,160
Last night,

238
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,680
after your dad left,

239
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:58,000
what were you and your mom doing?

240
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:04,920
Last night, my mom

241
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:06,980
was helping me practice the guzheng.

242
00:12:08,160 --> 00:12:09,000
Really?

243
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,600
I just asked the neighbors.

244
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,520
They all said

245
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:16,450
they didn't hear you playing the guzheng last night.

246
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,600
No.

247
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,680
I did play.

248
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,320
My mom supervises me every night.

249
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,240
Yijun.

250
00:12:31,040 --> 00:12:33,280
Children shouldn't lie.

251
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:35,640
You lied,

252
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,420
so I won't be able to find the bad guys.

253
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,800
I'm sorry, Inspector.

254
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,360
I lied just now.

255
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,440
Last night,

256
00:12:52,800 --> 00:12:55,260
I wasn't playing the Guzheng the whole time.

257
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:57,840
Yijun.

258
00:12:59,040 --> 00:12:59,640
Yijun.

259
00:13:00,080 --> 00:13:00,760
Wake up.

260
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:03,770
Why aren't you practicing?

261
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:06,880
I was too sleepy,

262
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,360
so I fell asleep.

263
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:13,920
Forget it.

264
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:16,440
Remember this.

265
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:18,300
No matter who asks,

266
00:13:18,960 --> 00:13:20,560
say that I was practicing with you at night.

267
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:21,360
Do you hear me?

268
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:31,320
It's okay.

269
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,980
Being honest makes you a good boy.

270
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:39,920
Be honest.

271
00:13:40,480 --> 00:13:41,940
Where were you last night?

272
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:43,200
Last night.

273
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:46,000
Last night, Dachuan went to find Leng Fang.

274
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,200
I followed him.

275
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:50,600
Dachuan.

276
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:53,370
Let's go to the police station.

277
00:13:55,280 --> 00:13:56,680
We can't go to the police.

278
00:13:56,760 --> 00:13:58,120
If we do, Tongtong won't come back.

279
00:13:58,120 --> 00:14:00,180
But where will you find her daughter?

280
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,400
She knows her.

281
00:14:01,400 --> 00:14:02,480
You can't fool her.

282
00:14:04,680 --> 00:14:05,610
We'll find a way.

283
00:14:06,200 --> 00:14:07,280
There must be a way.

284
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:11,930
Where are you going?

285
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:13,640
I'm going to the police station.

286
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,840
There's no other way.

287
00:14:15,160 --> 00:14:15,720
If I don't go now,

288
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,760
we might really lose Tongtong forever.

289
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:19,240
You can't go to the police station.

290
00:14:19,240 --> 00:14:20,840
I'm done for if you go there.

291
00:14:21,280 --> 00:14:22,320
Turn yourself in.

292
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,360
This is retribution.

293
00:14:25,520 --> 00:14:26,280
If you hadn't done

294
00:14:26,280 --> 00:14:28,040
so many wicked things,

295
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,440
how could Tongtong have been taken?

296
00:14:31,880 --> 00:14:32,480
Come back.

297
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:33,960
We're husband and wife.

298
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:35,400
You can't drive me to my death.

299
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:37,400
Do you want to end the Gu family line?

300
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:43,800
We're husband and wife.

301
00:14:43,800 --> 00:14:45,520
Can't you leave me a way out?

302
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:47,540
Tongtong is my only child.

303
00:14:47,640 --> 00:14:49,200
I will bring him back. Do you understand?

304
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:50,560
Tongtong is my own son.

305
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:55,400
I'm bringing him back.

306
00:14:55,880 --> 00:14:57,140
I'm bringing him back.

307
00:15:06,240 --> 00:15:07,000
Dachuan.

308
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:08,960
Dachuan.

309
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:12,680
Dachuan.

310
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:14,240
Dachuan.

311
00:15:15,200 --> 00:15:17,000
I realized he wasn't breathing.

312
00:15:17,160 --> 00:15:18,520
I was so scared,

313
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,120
so I ran back to the shop.

314
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:23,320
So Gu Dachuan died by accident.

315
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:29,080
I didn't know it would turn out like this.

316
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:31,010
It really has nothing to do with me.

317
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:34,080
Since you didn't kill him,

318
00:15:34,520 --> 00:15:36,160
when we went to see you that day,

319
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:37,820
why didn't you tell the truth?

320
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:39,920
I...

321
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:42,890
I was afraid of being taken for the killer.

322
00:15:43,280 --> 00:15:45,200
I was involved in that matter,

323
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:49,010
and I was afraid I wouldn't be able to explain myself.

324
00:15:49,840 --> 00:15:51,040
Officers,

325
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:53,800
I've explained everything clearly.

326
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:54,920
Can I go home now?

327
00:15:55,320 --> 00:15:55,920
Mrs. Gu,

328
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:57,640
a life is at stake.

329
00:15:57,640 --> 00:15:59,640
Before the case is cleared up,

330
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:01,800
please stay at the police station to assist us.

331
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:02,520
But,

332
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:04,520
Yijun is still at home alone.

333
00:16:23,560 --> 00:16:24,360
Yijun.

334
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:30,040
Is he really not home?

335
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:34,960
Yijun.

336
00:16:41,280 --> 00:16:41,920
Yijun.

337
00:16:42,440 --> 00:16:43,600
Are you upstairs?

338
00:16:47,640 --> 00:16:48,360
Yijun.

339
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:52,000
Just now,

340
00:16:52,080 --> 00:16:54,120
why didn't you answer when I called?

341
00:16:56,040 --> 00:16:58,440
Did you take my mom away?

342
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,160
No.

343
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:05,210
Your mom is helping us with an investigation.

344
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:07,680
Look,

345
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:10,280
she asked us to bring this to you.

346
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:19,240
Your mother

347
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:21,680
might have to stay at the police station for a few more days.

348
00:17:21,680 --> 00:17:23,410
She asked us to come pick you up.

349
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:28,480
Do you blame us

350
00:17:28,480 --> 00:17:30,080
for taking your mother away?

351
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,400
I know you did it to catch the bad guys.

352
00:17:36,320 --> 00:17:37,320
It's all my fault.

353
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,120
If I hadn't insisted on going out

354
00:17:39,120 --> 00:17:40,640
that day,

355
00:17:42,200 --> 00:17:44,930
my little brother wouldn't have been kidnapped,

356
00:17:45,160 --> 00:17:46,690
and Dad wouldn't have died.

357
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,320
Don't cry.

358
00:17:58,520 --> 00:17:59,650
It's not your fault.

359
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:18,960
It's okay.

360
00:18:21,840 --> 00:18:23,040
Come with me.

361
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:25,360
You're turning into a little dirtball.

362
00:18:25,720 --> 00:18:26,400
Come here.

363
00:18:27,760 --> 00:18:28,520
Come here.

364
00:18:28,520 --> 00:18:29,320
What's wrong?

365
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,240
I'm giving him a bath.

366
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,040
Look how dirty he is.

367
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:31,970
Hold this for me.

368
00:18:32,960 --> 00:18:33,840
Come in and help me.

369
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:35,160
Hurry up. Get inside.

370
00:18:35,800 --> 00:18:36,660
Close the door.

371
00:18:39,040 --> 00:18:40,360
I don't want a bath.

372
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,100
What are you doing?

373
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:47,680
This little brat.

374
00:18:48,360 --> 00:18:49,320
He's taking a bath.

375
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,240
A grown man.

376
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,680
I used to hate bathing so much,

377
00:18:51,680 --> 00:18:52,160
but I never said a word.

378
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:52,960
Bao,

379
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:54,760
do you think it's possible...

380
00:18:54,760 --> 00:18:55,360
Possible what?

381
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:56,280
You can't just not bathe.

382
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:56,880
What if...

383
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:58,160
maybe.
